---

<aside class="stock-notice" role="note" aria-label="Aviso sobre preços e disponibilidade">
	<div class="stock-notice-icon" aria-hidden="true">
		<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
			<path
				d="M22 12C22 6.47715 17.5228 2 12 2C6.47715 2 2 6.47715 2 12C2 17.5228 6.47715 22 12 22C17.5228 22 22 17.5228 22 12Z"
				stroke="currentColor"
				stroke-width="1.5"></path>
			<path d="M12 11V16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
			<circle cx="12" cy="8" r="0.75" fill="currentColor"></circle>
		</svg>
	</div>
	<p class="stock-notice-text">
		Os preços dos notebooks seminovos começam a partir de <strong>R$ 1.199,00</strong>. Os modelos
		exibidos no site estão sujeitos à disponibilidade de estoque no momento do contato — fale com a
		gente no WhatsApp para confirmar o modelo e o valor atual.
	</p>
</aside>

<style>
	.stock-notice {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 0.875rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		padding: 1rem 1.125rem;
		border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent-text) 28%, white);
		border-radius: 0.875rem;
		background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 12%, white);
	}

	.stock-notice-icon {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		width: 1.5rem;
		height: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 0.1rem;
		color: var(--color-accent-text);
	}

	.stock-notice-icon svg {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
	}

	.stock-notice-text {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
		color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-text) 88%, white);
	}

	.stock-notice-text strong {
		color: var(--color-text);
		font-weight: 600;
	}
</style>
